==English==

===Noun===
'''ballast'''
#[[heavy|Heavy]] [[material]] that is placed in the [[hold]] of a [[ship]] (or in the [[gondola]] of a [[balloon]]), to [[provide]] [[stability]]
#[[coarse|Coarse]] [[gravel]] or similar material [[laid]] to form a [[bed]] for [[road]]s or [[railroad]]s

====Translations====
* [[Ido]]: [[balasto]]
* Dutch: [[ballastbed]]

===Transitive verb===
'''to ballast'''
#To [[stabilize]] or [[load]] a ship with ballast
#To lay ballast on the bed of a railroad track

